# No aria-label

Do not add `aria-label`, `aria-labelledby`, or other `aria-*` attributes to elements in this project.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<button aria-label="Select red color">...</button>

// ✅ GOOD
<button title="red">...</button>
```
